e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"How Good Manufacturing Practices meet the requirements of ISO 9001:2015 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Has your company been using GMPs (Good Manufacturing Practises)? If the response is yes, be aware that there is an additional benefit that you might have"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"ISO 9001 certification consultant in Dubai, ISO 9001 certification in Dubai, ISO 9001 certification in UAE"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"How Good Manufacturing Practices meet the requirements of ISO 9001:2015 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"Has your company been using GMPs (Good Manufacturing Practises)? If the response is yes, be aware that there is an additional benefit that you might have"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/how-gmp-meet-the-requirements-of-iso-9001-2015-certification"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:00+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"How Good Manufacturing Practices meet the requirements of ISO 9001:2015 Certification | WIZMS"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Has your company been using GMPs (Good Manufacturing Practises)? If the response is yes, be aware that there is an additional benefit that you might have"}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1b","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Processes"}]
11:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The need for documented procedures and recurring audits is emphasized by both GMP and the ISO 9001 Standard. To achieve compliance, a company should have standardized procedures that are well-documented and conveyed to the staff."}]
12:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Having established processes makes it simpler to monitor and examine deviations as well as to identify and control risks. Additionally, it encourages effective knowledge transfer and guarantees that the company can uphold quality at each stage of the process."}]
13:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Procedures"}]
14:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 7.5 of ISO 9001 and GMP both mandate that the business document its practises in addition to the prior topic. These may include instructions, procedures, flowcharts, and steps for carrying out crucial tasks or processes."}]
15:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Consistent results are ensured by having documented procedures since any substantial manufacturing-related variations can be quickly tracked down, analysed, and corrected. These are frequently referred to as standard operating procedures (SOPs). Operators must be trained to complete the necessary records for traceability in an accurate and timely manner during these processes."}]
16:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Premises and Equipment"}]
17:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The work environment must meet the requirements of ISO 9001 Clause 7.1.4. By describing the conditions essential for facility management, GMP connects to this requirement. Manufacturing businesses should make an effort to design their buildings and machinery so that adequate cleaning and cross-contamination are possible."}]
18:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Having a maintenance and calibration programme in place is another requirement of the ISO 9001:2015 Standard for the company. This is essential for the confirmation and verification of results, particularly those from laboratory tests."}]
19:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Hire best ISO certification consultant in UAE, Dubai or call us at 00971526325363 right away to learn more about how your GMP can assist your company with becoming certified to the ISO 9001:2015 certification in Dubai, UAE or send us an email."}]
1a:["$","footer",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 9001 certification consultant in Dubai"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 9001 certification in Dubai"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded","children":"ISO 9001 certification in UAE"}]]}]}]
